---
// No props — static copy per design spec
---

<section
  class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-[72px] px-10 pt-20 pb-16 max-w-[1200px] mx-auto"
>
  <!-- Left column: kicker + tagline -->
  <div class="flex-1">
    <p
      class="mb-6"
      style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-meta);"
    >
      pasqualo.to · 2025–26
    </p>
    <h1
      style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 48px); font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1.1; color: var(--color-ink);"
    >
      Photography and personal work<br />
      by <em style="color: var(--color-accent);">Augusto Pasqualoto</em>.
    </h1>
  </div>

  <!-- Right column: bio note -->
  <div
    class="md:w-[260px] shrink-0 flex flex-col justify-end"
    style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-meta);"
  >
    <p>
      The shop is a side project — I photograph public events and people doing
      things they love, and let them find themselves afterwards.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-3">
      The main site is the personal stuff: friends, pets, trips.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
